## ğŸŒŸ **Features**
âœ”ï¸ **Chat with AI Doctor** - Get AI-generated medical responses via chat.  
âœ”ï¸ **Talk with AI Doctor** - Interact using voice commands and listen to AI-generated responses.  
âœ”ï¸ **Medical Report Analysis** - Upload PDFs for AI-powered analysis.  
âœ”ï¸ **Multilingual Support** - Supports English, Hindi, Spanish, French, and German.  
