âœ”ï¸ **Password Reset via Email** - Secure password recovery system.  
âœ”ï¸ **AWS Polly Integration** - Converts AI-generated text into speech.  
âœ”ï¸ **AWS Comprehend Medical** - Extracts medical entities from user input.  

